🍔 Food Panda Clone

A || Food Panda Clone || that replicates the basic structure and functionality of the popular food delivery platform | Food Panda |. This project showcases a responsive UI with various features like restaurant listings, food categories, cart functionality, and more.

---

📋 Features

- 🍕 || Restaurant Listings || Browse through different restaurants with their menu items.
- 🛒 || Cart System || Add and remove items to/from your cart.
- 🗺️ || Location-based Search || Filter restaurants based on the user's location.
- 🖥️ || Responsive Design || Mobile and desktop-friendly UI.
- 💳 || Order Summary || View details of selected items before finalizing an order.
- 🏠 || Home Page || Featured restaurants, search functionality, and categories.
- 🍔 || Food Categories || Filter restaurants by cuisine (e.g., Italian, Chinese, etc.)

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5 – Structure and layout  
- CSS3 – For styling, animations, and responsive design  
- JavaScript (ES6) – For user interactivity and cart functionality  
- Vercel – Hosting and deployment (optional)

